 #3f3f3f; font-size: calc(16px * 1.1); font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2;">2. MaxClaw（MiniMax版）</h3><p class="p" style="margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;"><strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">厂商</strong>：MiniMax（国内最早一批云端化方案）\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">官网</strong>：agent.minimaxi.com\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">定位</strong>：主打国内模型优化，一键云端部署\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">适合人群</strong>：不想自己部署、追求稳定性的用户</p><h3 class="h3" data-heading="true" style="padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-size: calc(16px * 1.1); font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2;">3. Kimi Claw</h3><p class="p" style="margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;"><strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">厂商</strong>：月之暗面（Moonshot AI）\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">官网</strong>：kimi.com/bot\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">定位</strong>：基于 Kimi K2.5，主打长文本理解和多轮对话\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">适合人群</strong>：需要处理长文档、深度研究的用户</p><h3 class="h3" data-heading="true" style="padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-size: calc(16px * 1.1); font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2;">4. CoPaw（阿里版）</h3><p class="p" style="margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;"><strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">厂商</strong>：阿里巴巴（通义实验室）\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">定位</strong>：开源桌面 Agent 工具，支持本地与云端双部署\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">核心特点</strong>：模块化设计（Prompt、Hooks、Tools、Memory 解耦），支持自定义 Skills\ <strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-si